Package: cdrcR
Title: Retrieve data from the CDRC APIs
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Alessia",
           family = "Calafiore",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "aelissa3388@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5953-2891"))
Description: A wrapper for the CDRC APIs that returns data frames or sf of 
	CDRC data. Available datasets include the AHAH index, the 2019 Multidimensional Deprivation Index, the Internet User Classification, the Output Area Classification.
